<br>
Also, this makes the higher %mod skill items useless after you get high enough in skill (eg the 15% tailoring item, would in effect do the same as the 5% once you reach 250 skill in tailoring).<br>
<br>
Due to the randomness of skill increases/combines its probably best to go with your gut feeling about whats best for you.<br>
